<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0c8a3c5f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9"><num value="80r–9">§ 80r–9.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3c60-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Smithsonian Institution to carry out this subchapter, other than sections 80r–5(b) and 80r–6 of this title—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0c8a3c61-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $17,000,000 for fiscal year 2004; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0c8a3c62-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> such sums as are necessary for each fiscal year thereafter.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3c63-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Availability</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Amounts made available under subsection (a) shall remain available until expended.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3c64-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–9/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> Use of funds for fundraising</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Amounts appropriated pursuant to the authorization under this section may be used to conduct fundraising in support of the Museum from private sources.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id0c8a3c65-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/184/s11">Pub. L. 108–184, § 11</ref>, <date date="2003-12-16">Dec. 16, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/2682">117 Stat. 2682</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
